uote":{"pid":"473e8cf83112245f09d51defff10d766d5b43dfc","tid":689771,"uid":146494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2c8cd61693972d77dc5ec90f7deed5fd11884f","tid":689771,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"你咩科先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"係咪pass咗就升到上去?<br />\n應該science foundation"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"唔同科唔同分，見Social Science有啲Major 60/65就升到<br />\n我有個Flatmate想Degree讀Psycho<br />\n要求好似係70分<br />\n睇你Major係咩<br />\nOffer Letter會寫要幾分<br />\n<br />\n同埋要過學校個英文考試<br />\n不過第一個Sem過唔到第二個Sem可以補考<br />\n再唔得可以考IELTS<br />\n<br />\n不過整體嚟講唔算容易<br />\n因為聽講Assignment比親都係6X，做得好好先會有7字頭<br />\n佢地都有人驚Pass唔到有再報其他U<br />\nSem 2幾多功課幾Chur<br />\n不過佢地係1月入學嘅<br />\n<br />\n如果你真讀你唔好交買書(課本)錢<br />\n我話你知邊到有得免費拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e612658433944181794bda5dc72f39219ad1bc","tid":689771,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"升學率高係真嘅<br />\n聽講Manchester得40%<br />\nBirmingham唔知<br />\n<br />\n我讀Psycho個Flatmate覺得好輕鬆好有信心<br />\n佢仲要係中國嘅<br />\n之前Bio Chem全部用中文讀<br />\n但佢平時有溫下書咁成績都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n另一個Business Flatmate就報咗另一啲學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為覺得自己升唔到<br />\n<br />\n不過間學校真係好寬容<br />\n聽佢地講最後如果你達唔到平均分(爭少少)<br />\n除咗有得Argue(前提係你平時功課OK而且高出席率)<br />\n仲有一次機會比你重新寫最低分個份Assignment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以都讀得過嘅我諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41892c3689e44cf7a6564ee626b3c9acbc9b6739","tid":689771,"uid":146494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24bffd225ae1b487350e83c0be7ffea4402fc7d","tid":68