edBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"我而家讀緊第一年alevel 唔想再讀書所以轉去foundation<br />\n考咗IELTS啦有7 報個時同咗agent講我degree都係想讀psycho 一出出兩個offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打真係好打咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T20:52:52.000Z","msg":"唔想再讀書嘅話不如返香港算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}